18eb66cc85d56c02.body:
( https://tome.app/?utm_campaign=Warm+Welcome+3.0&utm_content=New+Warm+Welcome+HTML&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io )

Three Ideas to Get You Started

( https://tome.app/?utm_campaign=Warm+Welcome+3.0&utm_content=New+Warm+Welcome+HTML&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io )

Three Ideas to Get You Started

Shape and share ideas of all sizes

( https://tome.app/?utm_campaign=Warm+Welcome+3.0&utm_content=New+Warm+Welcome+HTML&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io )

Hi Sai,

Tome is a new way to shape and share your ideas. And it works best on desktop. If you haven’t already, open tome.app ( https://tome.app?utm_campaign=Warm+Welcome+3.0&utm_content=New+Warm+Welcome+HTML&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io ) on a computer to get the full experience.

So, what now? Here are three ways to get a sense of what you can do with Tome.

For Work: Sales & Fundraising Pitches

You can generate entire presentations with Tome. You’ll start with an outline you use as a starting point. Then edit and add your own content until you nail your point.

Choose command: Create presentation…
Start your prompt with: Sales pitch for…

Demo ideas:

* A mobile food delivery app in India
* Luxury perfume in Brazil
* Rollerskates in the UK

Create a presentation ( https://tome.app?utm_campaign=Warm+Welcome+3.0&utm_content=New+Warm+Welcome+HTML&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io )

For Exploration: Fact Sheets

Exploring a new topic? Generate a page and you’ll get four options to choose from, each exploring a different side of the subject and visual approach.

Command: Create page…
Example Prompt: Fact sheet about…

Demo ideas:

* Butterfly metamorphosis
* The history of coffee
* Moore’s law

Create a page ( https://tome.app?utm_campaign=Warm+Welcome+3.0&utm_content=New+Warm+Welcome+HTML&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io )

For Everything Else: Templates

Tome templates give you polished, professional outlines for all kinds of work.

You can find templates on your Templates tab ( https://tome.app/?tab=templates&utm_campaign=Warm+Welcome+3.0&utm_content=New+Warm+Welcome+HTML&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io ) or on the Tome website ( https://tome.app/templates?utm_campaign=Warm+Welcome+3.0&utm_content=New+Warm+Welcome+HTML&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io ).

Browse templates ( https://tome.app/templates?utm_campaign=Warm+Welcome+3.0&utm_content=New+Warm+Welcome+HTML&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io )

Want to dive deep? Check out the Getting Started Guide ( https://tome.app/tomecommunity/tome-getting-started-guide-cl5sigulu1899274x5iqictrjgv?utm_campaign=Warm+Welcome+3.0&utm_content=New+Warm+Welcome+HTML&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io ). To make work you truly love you’ll need to edit your tome, add to it, and make it your own.

Let’s make something great,
Keith & Henri

Tome is a new medium for shaping and sharing ideas.
Magical Tome, Inc., 600 Townsend Street Suite 125, San Francisco, CA 94103

To view this email as a web page, go to the following address: https://u3528416.ct.sendgrid.net/ls/click?upn=u001.g2DXLgXBUJK96crKtJKHYJhdQzWUwevCcpkVZ-2BwQnMoi8Zg9SRyeNlXUkln8cY2wucB3LzEEBX3DfDxdPMoiyk4HIZqvpbpV2EyUNLcpmv66fQuGXsLnkS3GAyrDnHEoKhUHG-2BtYGAhQzQlOzcuP-2Fy-2FCsL3h5PrA26Q6dVRIxLz4y9dOAIKaAIYXb5LP3oXnAfzqWhQoVoA6iskcMVRghhPSbgLl2hzdvsfMO0G83qJWgFLRz2loOgd83rVe1QsoyouRgjjOpvFOP64fmE-2B-2F2UeBArNB4DAcr7xp3gVW4vA-3Do_xE_4Swj1p5-2FCgDLdBYRfWMHjNmF1dwHQGMjuJurxNpcIHvkkxNALN21MGWkmx9Xp9M0ncGqjyYcHPUtP65HT3YtZTuGKK6Ah6x3WasKZ1mwKj3yPPT2uO0XaPNI5rVxSt2F0LLBt-2BC-2BlH-2BwbVQmc86gPzSyHhrVvcrWZNicM98B26TCQ266IyHBx04ddw8ZT7MDWl7RPbyyapVBhuDBBoWjjA-3D-3D

Welcome to the last edition of the Developer Digest of the first quarter of 2024 (the March 2024 edition, if you're counting!). Isn't 2024 moving quickly?

We hope you enjoy the new Dev Digest template. We'll revise it slightly throughout the year, but hopefully, it helps you better find the posts and products you're interested in learning more about. And as always, check out the Twilio Blog and Ahoy for even more of the content you love.

And with the preamble done, let's Digest…

Send Domain-Bound One-Time Passcodes with Twilio Verify

Phishing attacks on one time passcodes often trick users into interacting with fake domains. Kelley Robinson shows how to use domain-bound SMS OTPs, which autocomplete only on your domain in iOS and Android. Keep it safe.

Google Releases New Compliance Dashboard
Struggling to make sure you're compliant with all Google's sender requirements? Thanks to Google's new dashboard, you can check your compliance status for everything from DMARC to one-click unsubscribes. Thanks Google.
Forecast the Weather With PHP and OpenWeatherMap

Tired of all the boring generic weather applications? Make your own. Follow along with Matthew Setter to learn how to build a simple weather forecast website with PHP and the OpenWeatherMap API. Let there be sun.

. Introducing Audio Processor APIs for Twilio Voice

Access raw audio input and modify audio data before sending it to Twilio. See use cases plus a noise cancellation integration with our launch partner, Krisp.ai.

Power High Quality Audio Experiences. Segment Profiles to the Edge for Real-time personalization

Twilio Segment's Pooya Jaferian shows us how you can use the Segment Edge SDK with Cloudflare Workers to customize your user interactions, and shares a few personalization strategies. Take it to the Edge.

How to Send a WhatsApp Verification Code

Some countries prefer messaging apps over SMS—so why not cater to their two-factor authentication preferences? Learn how to send WhatsApp verification messages with our Verify API. Yes, it's me.

Build a custom Twilio alerting system using Express.js, json-rules-engine, and MongoDB

Twilio's Vikhyath S shows how to build a fully customizable Twilio email alerting system using Express.js, json-rules-engine, MongoDB, and the Twilio Debug Events Webhook for when you need your alerting rules to go beyond Twilio Alarms. Let me know!

Twilio Wants to Hear From You

We've put together a 15-minute survey about your experience with Twilio, with a chance to win a $100 gift card. No purchase necessary. Void where prohibited. Rules.

Share your thoughts. If you love the Ahoy Digest, share it on X or follow us on social! 18e66f94b72cad6c.body:
Twilio Segment just launched our 5th annual Customer Data Platform Report. By examining trillions of data points from our platform, we’ll share the major trends we’ve observed over the past five years.  

 

The CDP Report 2024 answers questions like:

  • Why the data warehouse has been surging in popularity  
  • Which tools are growing fastest on the Twilio Segment platform.
  • How predictive AI is changing the face of customer engagement 

 

Why Download?

This isn’t just another report. It’s a blueprint for the future, packed with actionable insights designed to elevate your customer engagement strategy to new heights. 

Whether you're looking to refine your data-driven decision-making, enhance customer experiences, or stay ahead of the curve, the 2024 CDP Report is a must read.

18e3b3c0b9bb842c.subject: You’re Invited! Join Us for Level Up with Voice Intelligence: Monitoring Automated Call Performance with AI
18e3b3c0b9bb842c.body:
Hi Ravi,

Are you ready to level up your automated voice campaigns? In this webinar, we will expand beyond call centers and utilize virtual agents and Twilio’s Voice Intelligence services to summarize, analyze, and measure the success of a call. No human representatives required!


In the second part of this series, we will cover everything you need to get started, from configuring your virtual agent, to gathering call intent and analyzing the sentiments of your customers. By the end of this webinar you will be equipped with all of the knowledge you need to enhance your customer experience, powered by AI!

Come hang out with us on Wednesday, March 20th, at 10 AM PT | 1 PM ET for our event Level Up with Voice Intelligence: Monitoring Automated Call Performance with AI <https://u3528416.ct.sendgrid.net/ls/click?upn=u001.g2DXLgXBUJK96crKtJKHYILvaX7M6fauqf5QqJEW0CN4nzOJ-2BjxPDYnpBzDaW8gc84K3DksNrXCY5jKI-2FmpAAZ2XdrdhZqgns-2FI30bKyN1o5GwkUY-2FWN0KONaGfh0vCFEEh-2B3nDNURE7vdQCxicjuA1-2BSu-2B3yA-2FETJQebZH5EW4-3DYfqO_4Swj1p5-2FCgDLdBYRfWMHjNmF1dwHQGMjuJurxNpcIHsZBFxVQ8d-2Fn6E1u0RNXjRJwBLo18Zte2-2Bw0q30SnQO-2B395R5oDFB1Uo-2BwGK6Jv6TK0miOqJ5ELSm5E6U8jbdlfGwW6lzv66iBFR8YWeMbtcTPzjUM8ug9QH22eVQHdFYUOqnVEd7tZgvs5oS0-2BnLQix66LI6pm3NqkesOxjLc91g-3D-3D>, where you will learn everything you need to know about Voice Intelligence.

18e1a20539b28be8.subject: [Live Event] Level Up with Voice Intelligence: Monitoring Automated Call Performance with AI
18e1a20539b28be8.body:
Hi Ravi,

Are you ready to level up your automated voice campaigns? In this webinar, we will expand beyond call centers and utilize virtual agents and Twilio’s Voice Intelligence services to summarize, analyze, and measure the success of a call. No human representatives required!


In the second part of this series, we will cover everything you need to get started, from configuring your virtual agent, to gathering call intent and analyzing the sentiments of your customers. By the end of this webinar you will be equipped with all of the knowledge you need to enhance your customer experience, powered by AI!

Come hang out with us on Wednesday, March 20th, at 10 AM PT | 1 PM ET for our event Level Up with Voice Intelligence: Monitoring Automated Call Performance with AI <https://u3528416.ct.sendgrid.net/ls/click?upn=u001.g2DXLgXBUJK96crKtJKHYILvaX7M6fauqf5QqJEW0CN4nzOJ-2BjxPDYnpBzDaW8gcnrUDxQ-2FqcxkeIFNID2NYVpzkyPrQSxqqkamH0wT-2FM6z2FftalUd-2BbXfstem0-2BxFq1fqKB8Pq12U0jVFAod7Nd8oBIfMs90lvpKnV5nE-2B4Vg-3DgaXD_4Swj1p5-2FCgDLdBYRfWMHjNmF1dwHQGMjuJurxNpcIHsXrDE6-2BEZkDXgwsHz0KClgMpqHCT3E2AxRt5D09KWemJU-2FgzUTJTWqr0yow8vTdiJmxwkGQJMGpdw5JgWJgrUkOcSXNlM0LSJ9RhXRA-2FAUmANcmRh5ILF-2FrLQYiBoW9VQDNRn0zbQ9PAAk18DQwP9iP-2B4J2Ljrh5zQ-2BB5NgplIWw-3D-3D>, where you will learn everything you need to know about Voice Intelligence.

How AI Is Powering Meta’s Technologies

From gaming to productivity, there are few aspects of our lives that this technology doesn’t stand to benefit.
